rtly%20after%20takeoff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BA%20small%20number%20of%20passengers%20were%20provided%20with%20medical%20assistance%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryanair%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20passengers%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20flight%20travelling%20from%20Birmingham%20to%20Tenerife%20were%20injured%20after%20the%20aircraft%20encountered%20turbulence%20shortly%20after%20takeoff%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20return%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20flight%20FR1121%2C%20which%20departed%20Birmingham%20Airport%20on%20Sunday%2C%20turned%20back%20%26quot%3Bshortly%20after%20take-off%20due%20to%20air%20turbulence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20landed%20normally%20before%20passengers%20disembarked%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20terminal%2C%20where%20a%20small%20number%20of%20passengers%20were%20provided%20with%20medical%20assistance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20said.%20The%20flight%20later%20resumed%20its%20journey%20to%20Tenerife%2C%20departing%20again%20at%209%3A06%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight-tracking%20data%20from%20Flightradar24%20shows%20the%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20departed%20Birmingham%20at%20about%203%3A05%20p.m.%20on%20December%2028%2C%20about%2015%20minutes%20later%20than%20its%20scheduled%20departure%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight-tracking%20website%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20aircraft%20squawked%207700%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20it%20returned%20to%20Birmingham.%20The%20transponder%20code%20is%20a%20general%20emergency%20signal%20used%20by%20pilots%20to%20alert%20air-traffic%20controllers%20that%20the%20plane%20requires%20immediate%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20also%20descended%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20feet%20during%20the%20diversion%20back%20to%20Birmingham%2C%20according%20to%20Flightradar24.%20Flightradar24%20said%20on%20X%20that%20such%20a%20descent%20%26qu