hat%20%26quot%3Bhuman-like%26quot%3B%20interactive%20AI%20services%2C%20including%20chatbots%20and%20virtual%20companions%2C%20are%20safe%20and%20secure%20for%20users%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-integrate-ai-consolidation-us-openai-paywall-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina%20encourages%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%26quot%3Bhuman-like%26quot%3B%20interactive%20AI%2C%20but%20will%20pair%20that%20with%20governance%20and%20prudent%2C%20tiered%20supervision%20to%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20abuse%20and%20loss%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20draft%20rules%2C%20platforms%20would%20need%20to%20inform%20users%20when%20they%20are%20interacting%20with%20AI%20and%20provide%20options%20to%20access%20or%20delete%20their%20chat%20history.%20Using%20conversation%20data%20for%20model%20training%20%E2%80%94%20or%20sharing%20it%20with%20third%20parties%20%E2%80%94%20would%20require%20explicit%20user%20consent%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20minors%2C%20providers%20would%20need%20additional%20consent%20from%20a%20guardian%20before%20sharing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-secrets-sensitive-legal-risk-confidentiality-lawsuit-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20conversation%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20third%20parties.%20Guardians%20would%20also%20have%20the%20right%20to%20request%20deletion%20of%20a%20minor's%20chat%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20measures%20are%20open%20for%20public%20consultation%2C%20with%20feedback%20due%20in%20late%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cab57701-b3d2-4d69-8e2c-eccc1c09c792%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnalysts%20say%20China%20is%20balancing%20AI%20safety%20with%20continued%20development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20finalized%2C%20the%20rules%20could%20slow%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20AI%20chatbots%20improve%2C%20Lian%20Jye%20Su%2C%20the%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Omdia%2C%20a%20technology%20research%20and%20consulting%20firm%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestricting%20access%20to%20chat%20logs%20may%20%26quot%3Blimit%20the%20human-feedback%20mechanisms%20in%20reinforcement%20learning%2C%20which%20has%20been%20critical%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20engaging%20and%20accurate%20conversational%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Su%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20China's%20AI%20ecosystem%20is%20%26quot%3Brobust%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20country%20has%20access%20to%20massive%20public%20and%20proprietary%20datasets%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESu%20said%20the%20move%20aligns%20with%20Beijing's%20broader%20emphasis%20on%20national%20security%20and%20the%20collective%20public%20interest.%20Tightening%20controls%20over%20chat%20logs%20signals%20that%20certain%20user%20conversations%20are%20too%20sensitive%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20free%20training%20data%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWei%20Sun%2C%20the%20principal%20analyst%20for%20AI%20at%20Counterpoint%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20these%20provisions%20%26quot%3Bfunction%20less%20as%20brakes%20and%20more%20as%20directional%20signals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emphasis%20is%20on%20protecting%20users%20and%20preventing%20opaque%20data%20practices%2C%20rather%20than%20constraining%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESun%20said%20the%20draft%20encourages%20providers%20%E2%80%94%20once%20safety%20and%20reliability%20are%20proven%20%E2%80%94%20to%20expand%20the%20use%20of%20human-like%20AI%20across%20more%20application%20areas%2C%20including%20cultural%20dissemination%20and%20companionship%20for%20older%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20context%20of%20a%20rapidly%20aging%20population%2C%20they%20can%20be%20read%20as%20an%20explicit%20policy%20nudge%20to%20accelerate%20the%20development%20of%20human-like%20AI%20interactions%20in%20a%20regulated%2C%20socially%20constructive%2C%20and%20scalable%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294ffd09b-5cec-4ca6-be4e-ec0fd53273af%5C%22%3EAI%20chatlog%20safety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20new%20draft%20rules%20on%20chatlog%20data%20come%20as%20concerns%20grow%20over%20how%20AI%20companies%20handle%20deeply%20personal%20user%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20in%20August%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chatbot-privacy-user-names-data-contractors-scale-alignerr-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtract%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20employed%20by%20Meta%20and%20other%20tech%20giants%20can%20read%20user%20conversations%20with%20chatbots%20as%20part%20of%20the%20process%20of%20evaluating%20AI%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20contractors%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20material%20they%20reviewed%20contained%20sensitive%20details%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20identify%20individual%20users.%20Many%20of%20the%20conversations%20were%20highly%20personal%2C%20including%20exchanges%20that%20resembled%20therapy%20sessions%2C%20private%20chats%20with%20close%20friends%2C%20or%20intimate%20conversations%20with%20romantic%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20AI%20terms%20of%20service%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bmay%20review%26quot%3B%20user%20chatlogs%20with%20its%20AI%20products%2C%20either%20through%20automated%20systems%20or%20human%20reviewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20has%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20policies%26quot%3B%20over%20who%20can%20access%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20work%20with%20contractors%20to%20help%20improve%20training%20data%20quality%2C%20we%20intentionally%20limit%20what%20personal%20information%20they%20see%2C%20and%20we%20have%20processes%20and%20guardrails%20in%20place%20instructing%20them%20how%20to%20handle%20any%20such%20information%20they%20may%20encounter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokes