n%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20was%20based%20in%20California%2C%20but%20I%20was%20working%20from%20London.%20Not%20even%20a%20year%20into%20my%20job%2C%20I%20was%20asking%20if%20I%20could%20be%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20after%20getting%20hired%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20Google%20transferred%20me%20to%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Then%2C%20a%20year%20after%20that%2C%20I%20quit.%20I%20packed%20up%20my%20bags%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20London%20in%20just%20two%20weeks%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-deep-tech-startup-accelerator-the-engine-mit-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estartup%20accelerator%20program%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20worth%20the%20risk%2C%20even%20in%20this%20difficult%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3335626-0a3b-446c-aef3-cc4a0ce4babc%5C%22%3ELiving%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20was%20incredible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20Google%20in%202022%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20on%20the%20Google%20Pixel%20audio%20team.%20I%20enjoyed%20my%20job%2C%20but%20being%20in%20London%2C%20the%20physical%20distance%20turned%20minor%20questions%20into%20major%20delays.%20If%20I%20hit%20a%20blocker%20with%20a%20specific%20subsystem%2C%20I'd%20send%20a%20message%20and%20wait%2024%20hours%20for%20a%20reply%20due%20to%20time%20zone%20differences%2C%20or%20spend%20many%20late%20nights%20in%20chats%20with%20colleagues%20to%20unblock%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20was%20finally%20relocated%20to%20the%20Mountain%20View%20headquarters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-i-left-silicon-valley-california-after-two-years-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20almost%20exactly%20as%20I%20had%20always%20imagined%20it%20from%20movies%20and%20TV.%20California%20is%20the%20most%20beautiful%20place%20I've%20ever%20been%20to%2C%20and%20being%20able%20to%20call%20it%20my%20hom