0but%20there's%20another%20city%20in%20the%20US%20that's%20home%20to%20even%20more%20top%20influencers%20per%20capita%3A%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVale%20and%20Sebastian%20Genta%20understand%20why.%20The%20siblings%20and%20social%20media%20personalities%20moved%20back%20to%20their%20hometown%20of%20Miami%20in%202021%2C%20after%20spending%20five%20years%20in%20LA.%20The%20pair%2C%20who%20post%20about%20their%20glamorous%20lives%20and%20occasionally%20offer%20a%20wry%20take%20on%20influencing%2C%20wondered%20what%20their%20move%20would%20mean%20for%20their%20careers.%20They%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMiami%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Vale%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20events%20in%20Miami%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20people%20that%20are%20there%2C%20brands%20that%20are%20present%2C%20it's%20almost%20as%20much%20as%20LA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20us%20know%20each%20other%2C%20so%20if%20you%20go%20to%20events%20that%20Gucci%20is%20throwing%20at%20the%20Design%20District%2C%20you're%20more%20than%20likely%20going%20to%20bump%20into%20five%20to%2020%20familiar%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20Sebastian%20said%20of%20the%20upscale%20fashion%20and%20design%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223454%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MIAMI%2C%20FLORIDA%20-%20JUNE%2020%3A%20Vale%20Genta%20and%20Sebastian%20Genta%20attend%20CASA%20NEOS%20Grand%20Unveiling%20at%20Casa%20Neos%20on%20June%2020%2C%202024%20in%20Miami%2C%20Florida.%20(Photo%20by%20Alexander%20Tamargo%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20CASA%20NEOS%20by%20Riviera%20Dining%20Group%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694c591064858d02d2176366%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222591%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVale%20Genta%20and%20Sebastian%20Genta%20found%20Miami%20was%20a%20thriving%20creator%20city%20when%20they%20moved%20back%20in%202021.%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Tamargo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption