g%20on%20your%20budget%20and%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264e29f6e-7cf0-4762-818a-6c01dbb2bb2b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20upgrade%5C%22%3EBest%20upgrade%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOzlo's%20Sleepbuds%20are%20the%20priciest%20pair%20I%20tested%2C%20and%20while%20my%20experience%20was%20generally%20positive%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20say%20whether%20the%20additional%20features%20are%20worth%20the%20steep%20price%20tag.%20Like%20the%20Soundcore%20A30%2C%20the%20Sleepbuds%20are%20ergonomically%20designed%20to%20fit%20comfortably%20in%20your%20ear%2C%20and%20the%20four%20adjustable%20tip%20options%20allow%20for%20flexibility%20for%20most%20sleepers.%20The%20Sleepbuds%20boast%20passive%20noise%20cancellation%2C%20a%20similar%20sound%20quality%20to%20daytime%20earbuds%2C%20and%20Ozlo's%20paired%20app%20with%20a%20wide%20library%20of%20nature-like%20noise%20masking%20sounds.%20Bluetooth%20pairing%20was%20a%20bit%20spotty%3A%20Connecting%20the%20earbuds%20to%20my%20phone%20was%20fairly%20straightforward%20at%20first%2C%20but%20sometimes%20the%20Ozlo%20app%20would%20incorrectly%20indicate%20that%20the%20buds%20were%20disconnected%2C%20even%20when%20they%20were%20still%20connected%20to%20my%20device.%20This%20seemed%20to%20be%20hit%20or%20miss%3A%20Sometimes%20they'd%20connect%20to%20Bluetooth%20perfectly%2C%20and%20sometimes%20I'd%20spend%20a%20frustrating%20extra%20few%20minutes%20connecting%20the%20buds%20to%20my%20device%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Ozlo%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ozlo%20sleepbuds%20on%20orange%20bedding%20with%20a%20screenshot%20from%20the%20ap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694ed430832e0ef1ead6d818%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%2010-hour%20battery%20life%20will%20get%20you%20through%20the%20night%20with%20time