20convenient%20placement%20of%20the%20volume%20and%20power%20controls%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20mask%2C%20avoiding%20the%20need%20to%20reach%20for%20your%20phone%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20light%20sleepers%20like%20me%2C%20as%20fiddling%20with%20headbands%20and%20masks%20to%20make%20adjustments%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20would%20more%20likely%20wake%20me%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LC%20Dolida%20Sleep%20Mask's%20battery%20life%20holds%20a%20respectable%2010%20hours%20of%20use%2C%20and%20the%20sound%20quality%20was%20clear%20enough%20to%20fall%20asleep%20to%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20price.%20The%20mask%20stayed%20securely%20in%20place%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20any%20more%20obtrusive%20than%20an%20average%20sleep%20mask.%20Overall%2C%20it%20provides%20everything%20we'd%20expect%20from%20a%20budget%20pick.%20If%20you're%20not%20ordinarily%20a%20sleep%20mask%20wearer%20but%20are%20considering%20one%20with%20sound%2C%20the%20LC%20Dolida%20is%20a%20great%20starter%20pair%20as%20you%20learn%20your%20sleep%20style%20and%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d94d71c-bfe2-4077-b6ab-5a0e05af611c%5C%22%3EWhat%20else%20we%20tested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15116883775ck-20%26h%3Db3f911064823f7433a0b55ce9284de230ac5e26a43defa7dbde607e8b567d495%26postID%3D694ec24a946a298b9f878044%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-sleep-headphones%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FHoomBand-Bluetooth-Headphones-Headband-Meditation%252Fdp%252FB0BKCQTWGF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHoomband%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20This%20sleep%20headband%20boasts%20a%20wide%20library%20of%20meditations%20and%20sleep%20stories%2C%20in%20a%20soft%20and%20comfortable%20design.%20It's%20a%20decent%20choice%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20an