ergency%20if%20need%20be%2C%20but%20as%20Winter%20noted%2C%20sleep%20headphones%20are%20not%20designed%20to%20block%20out%20higher-pitched%20noises%20(like%20most%20emergency%20alarms).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1bbe937-f8ad-4f3d-9c1c-48d9f3e859e3%5C%22%3EApp%20features%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20available%20library%20of%20sleep%20sounds%20and%20meditations%2C%20a%20built-in%20alarm%20clock%2C%20and%20sleep%20analytics%20are%20some%20common%20features%20that%20could%20make%20a%20pair%20of%20sleep%20headphones%20stand%20out.%20All%20the%20pairs%20we%20tested%20connect%20to%20streaming%20apps%20like%20Spotify%20or%20Apple%20Music%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20listen%20to%20music%2C%20podcasts%2C%20or%20audiobooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d311d6f0-dd6a-4d9d-a145-1b973de16160%5C%22%3ECare%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMachine%20washability%20is%20a%20standout%20feature%20for%20a%20headband%20or%20mask%2C%20although%20not%20required%20for%20hygienic%20use.%20Consider%20ease%20of%20speaker%20removal%20and%20reinstallation.%20For%20earbuds%2C%20ensure%20you%20clean%20them%20regularly%20and%20refer%20to%20the%20specific%20cleaning%20instructions%20for%20each%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22105344c6-45b2-4f40-9423-38b661765342%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20each%20pair%20over%20at%20least%20seven%20days%2C%20considering%20the%20comfort%20of%20each%20pair%20for%20back%20and%20side%20sleepers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20general%20sound%20quality%2C%20battery%20life%2C%20connectivity%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20use%20throughout%20the%20night.%20I'm%20a%20light%20sleeper%2C%20and%20I%20sleep%20with%20a%20partner%20who%20wakes%20up%20quite%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20for%20work.%20I%20happened%20to%20move%20within%20NYC%20during%20the%20testing%20period%2C%20so%20I%20tested%20each%20pair%20in%20both%20a%20quieter%20residential%20apartment%20and%20a%20busy%20