20this%20was%20my%20first%20time%20visiting%20Hawaii%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20do%20as%20much%20research%20as%20possible%20before%20my%20trip.%20But%20after%20arriving%2C%20I%20still%20wished%20I'd%20known%20a%20few%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGetting%20around%20the%20island%20wasn't%20as%20tough%20as%20I%20expected%2C%20especially%20once%20we%20learned%20a%20handy%20tip.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clouds%20over%20palm%20trees%20on%20a%20shore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fbc2eec0c696569feaf18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMegan%20duBois%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20leaving%20for%20Oahu%2C%20I'd%20heard%20from%20friends%20and%20read%20on%20social-media%20groups%20that%20getting%20around%20could%20be%20difficult.%20My%20fears%20of%20sitting%20in%20traffic%20for%20the%20whole%20week%20set%20in%20before%20I%20even%20stepped%20foot%20off%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20never%20got%20stuck%20in%20gridlocked%20traffic%20over%20our%20six%20days%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-at-hotel-surprising-things-former-employee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehotel%20worker%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20met%20said%20that%2C%20no%20matter%20which%20part%20of%20the%20island%20you%20are%20on%2C%20the%20big%20secret%20to%20avoiding%20traffic%20is%20to%20head%20out%20after%209%20a.m.%20and%20try%20to%20make%20your%20way%20back%20either%20before%203%20p.m.%20or%20after%206%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20and%20I%20followed%20this%20rule%20every%20day%20of%20our%20trip%20and%20never%20had%20much%20traffic%20to%20deal%20with%20while%20we%20traveled%20from%20Ko%20Olina%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpearl-harbor-attack-2014-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPearl%20Harbor%3C%2