%20native%20trees%20help%20to%20use%20water%20wisely%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20and%20walk%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20map%20each%20site%20using%20KML%20Polygons%20%E2%80%94%20satellite-based%20tools%20that%20log%20the%20exact%20coordinates%20of%20every%20mini%20forest.%20This%20lets%20us%20maintain%20a%20digital%20record%2C%20verify%20locations%2C%20and%20track%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20forests%20are%20feeding%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20social%20impact%20matches%20its%20ecological%20gains.%20Beyond%20trees%2C%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418054%2Fneeti-goel-restaurateur-mumbai-khaanachiye-lb-trust-sundarbans-tiger-widows%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20Punjab.%20Around%20120%20people%20work%20at%20its%20nurseries%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20collaborates%20with%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20scale%20up%20plantations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20TBTP%20had%20generated%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20jobs%20through%20MGNREGA%2C%20most%20filled%20by%20women%20and%20young%20people.%20These%20roles%20extend%20beyond%20wages%2C%20involving%20environmental%20custodianship%20from%20land%20preparation%20to%20sapling%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMGNREGA%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20in%20local%20workers%20who%20not%20only%20earn%20but%20also%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20land.%20When%20someone%20helps%20raise%20a%20forest%20from%20scratch%2C%20it%20becomes%20personal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20watched%20yo